text:
Packers WR coach Jason Vrable on Amari Rodgers entering Year 2: "I feel really good about Amari. Cobby bumped me the other day and was like, 'Yo, you can feel it from him.' I just smiled. It's just the start." 

Said his confidence is building, things starting to click.
